LOCUS       Gateway_attP2            232 bp    DNA              UNK 01-JAN-1980
DEFINITION  Gateway (lambda-derived) attP2 attachment site; 232 bp, the
            specificity-2 donor-vector recombination site from pDONR221. The BP
            reaction (lambda Int + IHF) recombines it only with the cognate
            attB2 to give attL2 + attR2, enforcing directional recombinational
            cloning..
